About
A Legendary Venue with a Rich History
For over 40 years, Jannus Live has been the heart of live music in St. Petersburg, Florida. Nestled in downtown St. Pete, this open-air courtyard venue has hosted some of the biggest names in music—from Green Day and Red Hot Chili Peppers to Wu-Tang Clan and Ice Cube.
What started as Jannus Landing in 1984 quickly became a must-play venue for rising and legendary acts alike. Over the decades, Jannus Live has evolved, but one thing remains the same—the energy, the music, and the unforgettable experience.

Host Your Private Event at Jannus Live
Looking for a venue that’s unique, vibrant, and unforgettable? Jannus Live is available for private events! From corporate gatherings to wedding receptions, fundraisers, and private concerts, we’ve got the perfect space to make your event one to remember.
